def: Of or pertaining to the upper lip, or mustache.
Sewed or knit together; united by a suture; stitched.
The large succulent and slightly acid fruit of a small tree(Anona muricata) of the West Indies; also, the tree itself. It isclosely allied to the custard apple.
To embellish; to change fancifully; to present under newaspects, as of form, key, measure, etc. See Variation, 4.
The condition of being sulky; a sulky mood or humor; as, to bein the sulks.
The upward elevation of the crust of the earth, resulting froma geanticlinal.
The quality of being lethal; mortality.
The quality or state of being unequal; inequality; unevenness.Jer. Taylor.
